<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <h2 class="header color-secondary-text">Normalization</h2>
    <h3 class="caption flow-text">Be patient while we run a few algorithms over the information you provided, and hopefully you may gain some insight.</h3>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col s12">
      <p class="truncate">{{prettyRelationalSchema}}</p>
      <ul class="z-depth-3 collection">
        {{#each schema.fds as |fd|}}
          <li class="collection-item">{{fd.pretty}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3 class="header">Attribute/Key Analysis</h3>
  </div>
  {{#if model.specialKeys.necessary}}

    <div class="col s12">
      <h3 class="caption flow-text">Necessary Keys</h3>
      <ul class="z-depth-3 collection">
        {{#each model.specialKeys.necessary as |attr|}}
          <li class="collection-item">{{attr}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
  {{else}}
    <p class="color-secondary-text" style="text-decoration: line-through;">Necessary Keys</p>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if model.specialKeys.candidate}}

    <div class="col s12">
      <h3 class="caption flow-text">Candidate Keys</h3>
      <ul class="z-depth-3 collection">
        {{#each model.specialKeys.candidate as |attr|}}
          <li class="collection-item">{{attr}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
  {{else}}
    <p class="color-secondary-text" style="text-decoration: line-through;">Candidate Keys</p>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if model.specialKeys.middleGround}}
    <div class="col s12">
      <h3 class="caption flow-text">MiddleGround Keys</h3>
      <ul class="z-depth-3 collection">
        {{#each model.specialKeys.middleGround as |attr|}}
          <li class="collection-item">{{attr}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>{{else}}
    <p class="color-secondary-text" style="text-decoration: line-through;">MiddleGround Keys</p>
  {{/if}}
  {{#if model.specialKeys.useless}}
    <div class="col s12">
      <h3 class="caption flow-text">Useless Keys</h3>
      <ul class="z-depth-3 collection">
        {{#each model.specialKeys.useless as |attr|}}
          <li class="collection-item">{{attr}}</li>
        {{/each}}
      </ul>
    </div>
  {{else}}
    <p class="color-secondary-text" style="text-decoration: line-through;">Useless Keys</p>
  {{/if}}
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3 class="header">Generated Schemas</h3>
  </div>

  <div class="col s12">
    <h3 class="caption flow-text">Third Normal Form (3NF)</h3>
    <ul class="z-depth-3 collection">
      {{#each model.3nf as |attr|}}
        <li class="collection-item">{{attr}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </div>
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3 class="caption flow-text">Boyce-codd Normal Form (BCNF)</h3>
    <ul class="z-depth-3 collection">
      {{#each model.bcnf as |attr|}}
        <li class="collection-item">{{attr}}</li>
      {{/each}}
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3 class="header right-align">Thanks to Bernstein & Boyce Codd</h3>
    <p class="caption right-align">We can let a machine and a few clever algorithms do the hard parts of normalization for us.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12">
    <h3 class="header color-secondary-text left-align">And also to Webtask.io...</h3>
    <p class="caption flow-text left-align">...for letting us use their computing.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col s12 center-align">
    <p class="header">Not 100% sure the algorithms are correct, but I'll update any mistakes that are brought to my attention. May have to show them step-by-step. Check them out on GitHub if you're interested or think you could be able to help. =)</p>
    <a href="https://github.com/selbyk/fdAlgos.js" class="btn-large waves-effect waves-dark">{{fa-icon "github" size="lg"}} The Algorithms</a>
  </div>
</div>

{{outlet}}
